about.summary: A collection of dimensionality reduction techniques from R packages and a common interface for calling the methods.

name: r-dimred
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.2.3" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-dimred
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/dimRed_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/dimRed/dimRed_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e6e56e3f6999ebdc326e64ead5269f3aaf61dd587beefafb7536ac3890370d84

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 2
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-drr
    - r-magrittr
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-drr
    - r-magrittr

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('dimRed')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('dimRed')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/gdkrmr/dimRed
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  summary: A collection of dimensionality reduction techniques from R packages and a common interface
    for calling the methods.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
